This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with improving object detection model performance through data augmentation strategies. It also involves machine learning techniques such as iterative reinforcement learning, which suggests it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper may fall under the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category as it involves developing intelligent systems for object detection. The Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category is also a possibility as reinforcement learning is a type of neural network training. Finally, the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category is a possibility as object detection is a crucial component of many robotic systems.
